high_descs: Walk up to the toilet, then turn right and walk over to the left side of the counter.
Pick up the bottle of lotion off of the counter.
Turn right and walk towards the shower, then hang a right and walk up to the tub, turn left and walk over to the counter.
Open the left drawer below the counter and put the bottle of lotion inside, then close the drawer.
Turn around and walk up to the toilet.
Pick up the bottle of lotion off of the toilet tank.
Turn around and walk up to the counter.
Open the left drawer below the counter and put the bottle of lotion inside, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two bottles of lotion into a drawer.

high_descs: Face right and go to the left side of the sink cabinet that is in front of you.
Get the soap dispenser that is on the left side of the counter.
Turn to the right and cross the room to the sink near the end of the bathtub.
Put the soap dispenser in the bottom left drawer under the sink.
Go to the toilet behind you.
Pick up the soap dispenser from the back of the toilet.
Face the opposite direction to return to the sink near the end of the tub.
Put the soap dispenser into the same drawer as the other soap dispenser.
anns.task_desc: Move two soap dispensers to a drawer under a bathroom sink.

high_descs: Head to the counter on your right.
Pick up the soap on the counter.
Turn around, bring the soap to the other sink, left of the tub.
Put the soap in the left drawer under the sink.
Turn around, go to the toilet.
Pick up the soap on the toilet.
Turn around, go to the sink left of the tub.
Put the soap in the left drawer under the sink, behind the other soap.
anns.task_desc: Put two soaps in the left drawer under the sink next to the tub.
